# Step 1 — Memory Checklist

## Required

- Initialize project memory namespace under `~/.cursor/ai-brain/projects/<name>/`.
- Ensure `_index.md` exists with at least one entry row.
- Ensure at least one memory entry file exists.
- Apply category/status/namespace/tag rules from `brain-memory-kb`.

## Non-negotiable Gate

- Do not proceed to Step 2 or Step 3 until Step 1 is complete.
- If user asks to skip Step 1, refuse and continue Step 1.

## Verification Output

- `Memory verified: X entries in projects/<name>/`
